#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Advanced Gear"
msgstr "先進裝備"

#. ~ Description for Advanced Gear
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Extremely high-end items mod based around nanotech crafting and 3D printing,"
" with basic materials that can be found in labs, mutations to be added "
"later."
msgstr "基於納米科技製造和3D打印的極高階物品模組，基礎材料可在實驗室中找到，後續將添加變異內容。"

#: .\professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Nanotech Agent"
msgstr "納米科技特工"

#: .\professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Nanotech Agent"
msgstr "納米科技特工"

#. ~ Profession (male Nanotech Agent) description
#: .\professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"The nanotech project ALMOST finished in time to try to stop things.  But "
"almost doesn't quite cut it these days.  You were tasked with keeping the "
"prototypes safe, and trying to continue the research."
msgstr "納米科技項目幾乎及時完成以試圖阻止事態。但如今‘幾乎’並不夠用。你的任務是保護原型機安全，並嘗試繼續研究。"

#. ~ Profession (female Nanotech Agent) description
#: .\professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"The nanotech project ALMOST finished in time to try to stop things.  But "
"almost doesn't quite cut it these days.  You were tasked with keeping the "
"prototypes safe, and trying to continue the research."
msgstr "納米科技項目幾乎及時完成以試圖阻止事態。但如今‘幾乎’並不夠用。你的任務是保護原型機安全，並嘗試繼續研究。"

#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid "nanotech gear"
msgid_plural "nanotech gears"
msgstr[0] "納米科技裝備"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech gear'}
#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid "You shouldn't see this - nanogear"
msgstr "你不應看到此內容 - 納米裝備"

#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid "nanotech shield"
msgid_plural "nanotech shields"
msgstr[0] "納米科技護盾"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'nanotech shield'}.
#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid "Shield switched to active mode."
msgstr "護盾切換至主動模式。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech shield'}
#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid ""
"A large shield composed of a cluster of nanites, currently in passive mode, "
"you can block attacks with it.  When not in use, it compresses itself into "
"the handle."
msgstr "由納米機器人集群構成的大型護盾，當前處於被動模式，可用其格擋攻擊。不使用時，它會壓縮進手柄中。"

#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid "nanotech shield (active)"
msgid_plural "nanotech shield (active)s"
msgstr[0] "納米科技護盾（主動）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'nanotech shield (active)'}.
#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid "Shield switched to passive mode."
msgstr "護盾切換至被動模式。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech shield (active)'}
#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid ""
"A large shield composed of a cluster of nanites, currently in active mode, "
"it will automatically attempt to block attacks for you, allowing you to make"
" use of your hand.  When not in use, it compresses itself into the handle."
msgstr "由納米機器人集群構成的大型護盾，當前處於主動模式，將自動嘗試為你格擋攻擊，讓你能自由使用雙手。不使用時，它會壓縮進手柄中。"

#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid "nanotech 'mini-shoggoth' storage"
msgid_plural "nanotech 'mini-shoggoth' storages"
msgstr[0] "納米科技‘迷你修格斯’存儲裝置"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "nanotech 'mini-shoggoth' storage"}
#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid ""
"A large blob of nanites with an AI, it actively branches out pseudopods to "
"grasp items held near it and supports them as optimally as possible, "
"including reaching down and forming 'legs' to support itself if needed."
msgstr "一大團搭載AI的納米機器人，會主動伸出偽足抓取附近的物品並以最優方式支撐它們，包括在需要時向下延伸形成‘腿’來自我支撐。"

#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid "nanotech holster"
msgid_plural "nanotech holsters"
msgstr[0] "納米科技槍套"

#. ~ Use action holster_msg for {'str': 'nanotech holster'}.
#. ~ Use action holster_msg for {'str': 'nanotech sheath'}.
#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid "You store your %s"
msgstr "你存放了你的 %s"

#. ~ Use action holster_prompt for {'str': 'nanotech holster'}.
#. ~ Use action holster_prompt for {'str': 'nanotech sheath'}.
#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid "Store weapon"
msgstr "存放武器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech holster'}
#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid ""
"A small blob of nanites with an AI, it actively branches out pseudopods to "
"grasp guns held nearby it, and put them into the user's hands automatically "
"as needed."
msgstr "一小團搭載AI的納米機器人，會主動伸出偽足抓取附近的槍支，並在需要時自動將其放入使用者手中。"

#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid "nanotech sheath"
msgid_plural "nanotech sheaths"
msgstr[0] "納米科技刀鞘"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech sheath'}
#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid ""
"A small blob of nanites with an AI, it actively branches out pseudopods to "
"grasp blades held nearby it, and put them into the user's hands "
"automatically as needed."
msgstr "一小團搭載AI的納米機器人，會主動伸出偽足抓取附近的刀刃，並在需要時自動將其放入使用者手中。"

#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid "nanotech magazine holder"
msgid_plural "nanotech magazine holders"
msgstr[0] "納米科技彈匣夾"

#. ~ Use action holster_msg for {'str': 'nanotech magazine holder'}.
#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid "You store your %s."
msgstr "你存放了你的 %s。"

#. ~ Use action holster_prompt for {'str': 'nanotech magazine holder'}.
#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid "Store ammo"
msgstr "存放彈藥"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech magazine holder'}
#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid ""
"A small blob of nanites with an AI, it stores magazines and assists in "
"loading them as needed."
msgstr "一小團搭載AI的納米機器人，用於存儲彈匣並在需要時輔助裝填。"

#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid "nanosuit"
msgid_plural "nanosuits"
msgstr[0] "納米服"

