#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'nanotech ammo core (deathcloud)'}.
#: .\items\gear\nanotech_mags.json
msgid "You clear and reset your ammo core."
msgstr "你清空並重置了彈藥核心。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech ammo core (wire)'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech ammo core (dart)'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech ammo core (blade)'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech ammo core (deathcloud)'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech ammo core'}
#: .\items\gear\nanotech_mags.json
msgid ""
"An automated ammo production unit designed to process feedstock into usable "
"ammo as needed, complete with integrated power source.  Unfortunately, it "
"needs to be manually reset when emptied, and cannot be refilled by hand."
msgstr "一種自動彈藥生產單元，設計用於根據需要將原料加工成可用彈藥，並配有集成電源。不幸的是，清空後需要手動重置，且無法手動重新填充。"

