"Collection of nanites formed into a hollow container, a large portion of "
"their power is devoted to maintaining a cool temperature, leading to them "
"being immobile and blocking passage."
msgstr "由納米機器人組成的空心容器，其大部分能量用於維持低溫，導致無法移動並會阻擋通道。"

